      <h2 class="t-h2 t-balance">Humans moving through weather</h2>
      <p class="t-lead" style="text-align: left; max-width: 56ch;">A few of the seasons that often bring people here. You do not need to recognise yourself in a single one — most lives carry several at once.</p>
